      "cooked": "<p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/e/ed5113fdc427c61ec959ba9f535a12bfe933d6db.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"/uploads/short-url/xRoRUnp8h7dnmVowO5Gi2O7gppV.jpeg?dl=1\" title=\"passage%20real\"><img src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/e/ed5113fdc427c61ec959ba9f535a12bfe933d6db.jpeg\" alt=\"passage%20real\" data-base62-sha1=\"xRoRUnp8h7dnmVowO5Gi2O7gppV\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" data-dominant-color=\"B3B2AF\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">passage%20real</span><span class=\"informations\">1000\u00d71000 553 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>\n<p>Passage is a triple channel wideband signal mixer and voltage processor. The signal path is suitable for mixing any type of signal, including video, audio and low frequency sources.<br>\nEach channel of Passage applies a fixed bias and gain to the IN signal, where the bias can be added before (PRE) or after (POST) the gain, then sums this processed signal with the THRU input.</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5894-specifications-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5894-specifications-1\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Specifications</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Width, 10HP</li>\n<li>Mounting Depth, 32mm</li>\n<li>Power +12V @ 40mA</li>\n<li>Power -12V @ 40mA</li>\n</ul>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5894-videos-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5894-videos-2\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Videos</h1>\n<p>            <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLBj_H2oHy-6KClpDHfJfX-5af6SvzMUko&amp;wmode=transparent&amp;rel=0&amp;autohide=1&amp;showinfo=1&amp;enablejsapi=1\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"youtube-onebox\" seamless=\"seamless\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation\"></iframe>\n</p>\n<h1><a name=\"p-5894-other-resources-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-5894-other-resources-3\" aria-label=\"Heading link\"></a>Other Resources</h1>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://community.lzxindustries.net/tags/passage\">LZX Community forum posts tagged #passage</a></li>\n</ul>",
